Comment: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:06.27,Sign,,0,0,0,,{chapter}
Comment: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:15.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,A miserable romance {可哀想ね　ロマンス}
Comment: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,A tear-jerking nuance {涙誘うニュアンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:21.46,Sign,,0,0,0,,...another page of your memories, {想い出のページめくれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:24.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,Here she is - heroine of the past {追憶のヒロイン} {actually, "the heroine of the recollections" but that doesn't have a nice ring to it}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:36.07,Sign,,0,0,0,,I raise my eyes to your face - {あなたの面影　見上げて咲いている}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:39.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, I'm in full bloom {unsure, maybe "it's flourishing"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,A sunflower amidst the blizzard - {act. in the middle of winter}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,that would be me, my dear {真冬のひまわり　それが私なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:49.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,Always on the verge of freezing, {凍えるような気持ちでいつも}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,My feelings are out of control -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:57.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,Too stiff to even say "Do you still love me?" {「好き?」と尋くこともできず}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:02.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,My lips just keep wavering in this wind! {風に揺れていたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:07.24,Sign,,0,0,0,,A pitiful Romance {いじらしいね　ロマンス}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:10.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,Something that only happens in dreams: {夢のような出来事}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:14.28,Sign,,0,0,0,,Trying hard to forget, I fell even more in love {忘れるために愛したの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:17.05,Sign,,0,0,0,,with heroine of the past {追憶のヒロイン}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:21.87,Sign,,0,0,0,,Miracle that I came across now is hugging me tight {めぐりあえた奇跡　そっと抱きしめて}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:25.28,Sign,,0,0,0,,This is the story of my life, I'll do my best to protect it! {私だけの歴史　守ってゆくわ}
